#: admin/views/template_rm_frontend_primer.php:31
msgid "Using shortcode"
msgstr ""

#: admin/views/template_rm_frontend_primer.php:32
msgid ""
"Paste the form shortcode on the page or post where you want to display the "
"form. RegistrationMagic form shortcodes are in this format"
